com.mozilla.secops.parser

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mozilla.secops.parser.Event
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Event
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Represents a high level event after being processed by a Parser.

    After being parsed, all events are guaranteed to have an associated Payload value which contains information related to a specific type of event.

    Specific parser implementations may also add Normalized data fields to the event.

    See Also:
